{"tid":94853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"A貨特朗普金正恩出巡　維園年宵拜早年","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T17:00:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0685aa86c45fea06c4408841b60987302c6591","tid":94853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/photo/bkn-20170124212734087-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170124215530\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170124212734087-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170124215530&h=28273491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國新任總統「特朗普」大駕光臨維園年宵市場？仲有北韓領導人「金正恩」齊齊到年宵市場趁熱鬧？東網讀者伍先生表示，今日(24日)下午約6時許，見到「金正恩」和「特朗普」感到驚訝！後來才知是A貨領導人，仲有財神爺「傍住」一齊巡視維園，期間他們又向市民拜個早年。<br />\n<br />\n雖說是A貨，但幾個人打扮都十分神似，特別是「特朗普」，「真係好似樣！」他們三人一路巡視期間，不少途人都問他們來意，打算去邊處，但他們均一言不發。<br />\n<br />\n巡視期間，市民開始留意到三個主角出現，紛紛上前圍觀和拍照，但伍先生想同「領導人」自拍卻被左右保安人員攔阻：「唔准影」，令他甚感無癮，之後三人連同保安人員走過一些攤檔繼續「巡視業務」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/bkn-20170124212734087-0124_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170124%2Fbkn-20170124212734087-0124_00822_001.html&d=oudMuPEce2JXF3%2FcKJezMmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2c334281\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/bkn-20170124212734087-0124_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ccb041326e8efbae6274045d2de8095a4490041e","tid":94853,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"侵咁似ge 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04916254f9b348f8eb56f74180b245100a6d548a","tid":94853,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵咁似ge 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一向都係大眾臉鬼佬<br />\n<br />\n好多肥佬鬼佬 都同佢